<p>Thanks for a woodcut sent by ARW for <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Congratulations on his removal from London,</p> 
<p>and praise of his review of Francis Galton ["Hereditary genius", <hi rend="italic">Nature</hi> 1 (1870): 501–3]. CD agrees with every word of it.</p> 
